                            <summary>Ashkenazi semi-cursive (and cursive) script.</summary>
                            <handNote scope="major" script="ashkenazi" rend="semi-cursive">The name
                                Śimḥah - probably the name of the scribe - is frequently singled out
                                (e.g. fol. 71v), also in those glosses, which are written in a more
                                cursive script (e.g. 102r).</handNote>
                            <handNote scope="minor" script="ashkenazi" rend="cursive"/>
                        </handDesc>
