                    <history>
                        <origin>
                            <origPlace>[Northern Italy]</origPlace>
                            <origDate when="1450" calendar="Gregorian">[mid-15th century]</origDate>
                        </origin>
                        <provenance>Divorce letter dated AM 5192 (=1432 CE)on fol. 48v: <foreign xml:lang="he">"באחד בשבת בתשעה ועשרים יום לירח תמוז שנת חמשת אלפים
                                ומאה ותשעים ושנים ... כאן בבערן"</foreign>.</provenance>
                        <acquisition>The MS belonged to the collection of John Selden (1584-1654),
                            lawyer and historical and linguistic scholar and it was acquired by the
                            Library in 1659.</acquisition>
                    </history>
